  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "MPs get fuel from the army",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that necessary facilities have been provided for MPs coming to Parliament to get fuel from army camps in their areas of residence.",
        "According to a complaint made by a group of MPs to the Speaker that there is no system to get fuel for coming to Parliament, this facility has been provided to get fuel.",
        "Furthermore, Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe has instructed the Chief of Security Staff, the Commanders of the three armed forces and the Inspector General of Police to provide special police protection to all the MPs coming to the Parliament to participate in the voting to elect the new President."
      ],
